<sentence type="quasi">旧２信組事件</sentence>
<sentence>　<TIMEX3 type="DATE" value="1994" valueFromSurface="XX94">９４年</TIMEX3>に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e51">経営破たんした</EVENT>旧東京協和、旧安全の両信用組合の不正融資事件に<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e52">絡み</EVENT>、背任など４罪に<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e53">問われた</EVENT>元労相、<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t11" type="DURATION" value="P62Y" valueFromSurface="P62Y">６２</TIMEX3>）に対し、東京高裁は<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t12" type="DATE" value="2003-02-25" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-25">２５日</TIMEX3>、懲役<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t13" type="DURATION" value="P4Y" valueFromSurface="P4Y">４年</TIMEX3>の東京地裁判決（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t14" type="DATE" value="2000-03" valueFromSurface="XX00-03">００年３月</TIMEX3>）を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e54">破棄し</EVENT>、改めて懲役<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t15" type="DURATION" value="P3Y6M" valueFromSurface="P3Y6M">３年６月</TIMEX3>の実刑を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e55">言い渡した</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence type="fragment"><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>元労相は無罪を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e56">主張した</EVENT>が、安広文夫裁判長は４罪とも成立を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e57">認め</EVENT></sentence>
<sentence>「なりふり<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e58">構わず</EVENT>資金を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e59">調達しよう</EVENT>と<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e60">した</EVENT>利欲目的の犯行。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">国会議員の地位に<EVENT class="STATE" eid="e61">あり</EVENT>ながら、<EVENT class="NULL" eid="e62">不合理な</EVENT>弁解を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e63">繰り返し</EVENT>、反省も<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e64">していない</EVENT>」</sentence>
<sentence type="fragment">と<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e65">断罪した</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>元労相は<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e66">上告する</EVENT>方針。</sentence>
<sentence>　１審より<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e67">減刑した</EVENT>理由について安広裁判長は、詐欺の被害者である旧熊本工大（現<ruby rubyText="そう">崇</ruby><ruby rubyText="じょう">城</ruby>大学）側と<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t16" type="DATE" value="2003-02-04" valueFromSurface="XXXX-XX-04">今月４日</TIMEX3>に民事上の和解が<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e68">成立した</EVENT>ことを<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e69">あげた</EVENT>。</sentence>
<sentence>　元東京協和信組理事長の<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t17" type="DURATION" value="P57Y" valueFromSurface="P57Y">５７</TIMEX3>）＝控訴＝らと<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e70">共謀し</EVENT>て旧２信組から実姉の<delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete><delete type="copyright_note_by_author">■</delete>被告（上告中死亡）の<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e71">経営する</EVENT>企業に２７億円余を<EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e72">不正融資させた</EVENT>背任事件（<TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t18" type="DATE" value="1994" valueFromSurface="XX94">９４年</TIMEX3>）について、判決は<quote>「回収見込みが<EVENT class="STATE" eid="e73">ない</EVENT>ことを<EVENT class="I_STATE" eid="e74">熟知し</EVENT>ながら、信用組合側に融資を<EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e75">懇願した</EVENT>」</quote>と、その成立を<sampling type="end" /><EVENT class="I_ACTION" eid="e76">認めた</EVENT>。</sentence>
